sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Consumer
    participant P as Proxy
    participant R as Redis
    participant V as VPN Manager
    participant T as Target Host

    Note over V,T: Initially VPN tunnel UP
    C->>P: GET /service-a
    P->>R: GET vpn:status:profile-1
    R-->>P: "up"
    P->>T: Forward request
    T-->>P: Response
    P-->>C: 200 OK

    Note over V: VPN goes down
    V->>R: SET vpn:status:profile-1 "down"
    V->>R: PUBLISH vpn:events {"status":"down"}

    C->>P: GET /service-a
    P->>R: GET vpn:status:profile-1
    R-->>P: "down"
    P-->>C: 503 VPN Unavailable

    Note over V: VPN reconnects
    V->>R: SET vpn:status:profile-1 "up"
    V->>R: PUBLISH vpn:events {"status":"up"}

    C->>P: GET /service-a
    P->>R: GET vpn:status:profile-1
    R-->>P: "up"
    P->>T: Forward request
    T-->>P: Response
    P-->>C: 200 OK
